Package: DNABarcodeCompatibility_Shiny
Type: Package
Title: A Shiny interface for the DNABarcodeCompatibility package
Version: 0.99.0
Maintainer: Fabienne Wong Jun Tai <virginie.wong-jun-tai@pasteur.fr>
